item.title: CVE-2024-22027|2024-01-12T06:41:29.452Z -- AYS Pro Plugins -- WordPress Quiz Maker Plugin
item.description: Improper input validation vulnerability in WordPress Quiz Maker Plugin prior to 6.5.0.6 allows a remote authenticated attacker to perform a Denial of Service (DoS) attack against external services.
